## Framework Citations

This software implements and references established location science frameworks:

- Huff, D. L. (1964). "Defining and Estimating a Trading Area."
  Journal of Marketing, 28(3), 34-38.

- Reilly, W. J. (1931). The Law of Retail Gravitation.
  New York: Knickerbocker Press.

- Christaller, W. (1933). Die zentralen Orte in Süddeutschland.
  Jena: Gustav Fischer. (English translation: Central Places in Southern Germany, 1966)

- Applebaum, W. (1966). "Methods for Determining Trade Areas."
  Journal of Marketing Research, 3(1), 74-84.

These frameworks are in the public domain as academic works.
